>>>> 4.1 Why Docker Compose?
>>>> You could manually launch containers one by one.
>>>> That quickly becomes impossible to manage.
>>>>
>>>> Instead, every service in this book will have:
>>>>
>>>> docker-compose.yml
>>>> .env
>>>> README.md
>>>>
